org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.surrogate

Class LogarithmicNormalizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.surrogate.ModelInputNormalizer
      • org.pikater.core.utilities.evolution.surrogate.LogarithmicNormalizer

  • public class LogarithmicNormalizer
extends ModelInputNormalizer
    Performs a logarithmic transformation of the input values. First moves the interval in such a way that the lower limit is 1.0. Than computes the logarithm of the result.
    Author:
    Martin Pilat
